title: LearnBud AI
tasks: User Research & Testing, UI Design, Design Strategy
introduction: **LearnBud AI** is a modern mobile learning application designed to help students study smarter with the support of artificial intelligence. The app provides a complete digital learning experience where users can access courses, watch video lessons, generate AI-powered notes, attempt quizzes, track progress, and communicate with teachers — all within a sleek, futuristic dark-mode interface.
The goal of the project is to create an intuitive, visually immersive, and highly functional platform that makes learning easier, faster, and more engaging for students of all levels.
primaryGoals: Build an easy and fast login flow
Present lessons, quizzes, and assignments clearly
Include a social/interactive element (profiles, chats, progress tracking)

title: Workista
tasks: User Research & Testing, UI Design, Design Strategy
introduction: **Workiesta** is a modern job marketplace that connects talented freelancers with businesses looking for specialized services. The platform supports both web and mobile experiences, enabling users to explore job opportunities, apply easily, and communicate with employers efficiently.
Workiesta focuses on providing smarter job matching by analyzing user skills, preferences, and industry trends — helping people find meaningful jobs fast.
primaryGoals: Deliver a clean, modern, and professional interface that enhances user trust and usability.
Ensure a consistent design experience across web and mobile platforms for seamless user interaction.
Prioritize clarity and simplicity in UI components to improve navigation and reduce user friction.
Present data in a structured, intuitive way that supports faster decision-making.
Build a scalable design system with typography, color, and layout standards that maintain brand consistency.
Create visually engaging dashboards and workflows that balance aesthetics with functionality.
coreFeatures: User Dashboard : Personalized overview with quick insights and activity tracking.
Task & Workflow Management: Clean tables, sorting options, filters, and detailed task views.
Data Visualization: Graphs, stats, and analytics presented in a simple, readable format.
User Profile & Settings: Easily accessible and fully customizable profile management.
Notifications & Updates: Real-time alerts integrated seamlessly into the UI.
Responsive Web Layouts: Optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile experiences.
Mobile Application Screens: Complete end-to-end mobile flow for smooth on-the-go usage.
Component-Based Design System: Buttons, cards, form fields, icons, and color sets aligned with brand identity.
Secure Access & Authentication: Login, signup, user validation, and protected routing.
Footer Navigation & Quick Actions: Consistent structure to support fast interaction across pages.
